Dialogue: 3,0:29:23.90,0:29:24.60,T,atg1,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 3,0:29:25.90,0:29:26.63,JP,atg1,0,0,0,,しまった
Dialogue: 3,0:29:25.90,0:29:26.63,T,atg1,0,0,0,,糟了
