Dialogue: 3,0:32:15.29,0:32:15.87,T,atg1,0,0,0,,明
Dialogue: 3,0:32:17.20,0:32:17.88,JP,atg1,0,0,0,,明
Dialogue: 3,0:32:17.20,0:32:17.88,T,atg1,0,0,0,,明
Dialogue: 3,0:32:22.17,0:32:23.51,JP,atg1,0,0,0,,デーモンは死んだ
Dialogue: 3,0:32:22.17,0:32:23.51,T,atg1,0,0,0,,恶魔已经死了
Dialogue: 3,0:32:25.12,0:32:26.02,JP,atg1,0,0,0,,よくやった
Dialogue: 3,0:32:25.12,0:32:26.02,T,atg1,0,0,0,,干得好
Dialogue: 3,0:32:34.27,0:32:35.27,JP,atg1,0,0,0,,家へ帰ろう
Dialogue: 3,0:32:34.27,0:32:35.27,T,atg1,0,0,0,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 3,0:32:44.13,0:32:48.63,JP,atg1,0,0,0,,僕の両親は氷河で 何かに食われて死んだ
Dialogue: 3,0:32:44.13,0:32:48.63,T,atg1,0,0,0,,我的父母在冰川上 被什么东西吃掉了
Dialogue: 3,0:32:49.98,0:32:50.74,JP,atg1,0,0,0,,それも…
Dialogue: 3,0:32:49.98,0:32:50.74,T,atg1,0,0,0,,那难道也是…
Dialogue: 3,0:32:51.13,0:32:51.83,JP,atg1,0,0,0,,分からん
Dialogue: 3,0:32:51.13,0:32:51.83,T,atg1,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 3,0:32:53.26,0:32:53.99,JP,atg1,0,0,0,,分からんが
Dialogue: 3,0:32:53.26,0:32:53.99,T,atg1,0,0,0,,虽然不清楚但…
Dialogue: 3,0:32:55.26,0:32:55.83,JP,atg1,0,0,0,,多分
Dialogue: 3,0:32:55.26,0:32:55.83,T,atg1,0,0,0,,大概是
