Dialogue: 3,0:36:55.63,0:36:58.66,song,atg1,0,0,0,,Open The Gate Set Me Free
Dialogue: 3,0:36:55.63,0:36:58.66,songT,atg1,0,0,0,,打开那大门让我自由
